 299:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   * @brief Enable the I2C fast mode plus driving capability.
 300:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   * @param ConfigFastModePlus Selects the pin.
 301:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   *   This parameter can be one of the @ref I2CEx_FastModePlus values
 302:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   * @note  For I2C1, fast mode plus driving capability can be enabled on all selected
 303:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   *        I2C1 pins using I2C_FASTMODEPLUS_I2C1 parameter or independently
 304:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   *        on each one of the following pins PB6, PB7, PB8 and PB9.
 305:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   * @note  For remaining I2C1 pins (PA14, PA15...) fast mode plus driving capability
 306:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   *        can be enabled only by using I2C_FASTMODEPLUS_I2C1 parameter.
 307:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   * @note  For all I2C2 pins fast mode plus driving capability can be enabled
 308:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   *        only by using I2C_FASTMODEPLUS_I2C2 parameter.
 309:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   * @note  For all I2C3 pins fast mode plus driving capability can be enabled
 310:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   *        only by using I2C_FASTMODEPLUS_I2C3 parameter.
 311:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   * @retval None
 312:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   */
